title: Why does my phone autocall when i auto connnect to my car when pixel 2xl is connected to headphone?
content: I looked through my settings and see if there was something there ...but cant find anything. It happens 4x a week whenever i go to workout and have my skullcandy uproar wireless headphones still connected to my pixel 2XL. I wouldn't be phased but it always calls the same someone on my phone that i don't call unless ...its for work..lets put it that way...
